The host has gone offline, we are on the case.

As part of the product lifecycle management, We will end the Sales of Enterprise Cloud Databases services January 16th 2022 (no more new services). We will end the Growth of existing Enterprise Cloud Databases services May 16th 2022 (no more new nodes) We will end the Support of all Enterprise Cloud Databases services June 16th 2022 (shutdown of the services). Impacted customers will be notified by email and via control panel about this End-Of-Life process. We will cut-off the services the week before End of Support during punctual 2 hours time slot, to warn impacted customers. Perimeter: All PostgreSQL Enterprise Cloud Databases clusters, worldwide. Related product page: [FR] https://www.ovhcloud.com/fr/enterprise/products/enterprise-cloud-databases/ [EN] https://www.ovhcloud.com/en-ie/enterprise/products/enterprise-cloud-databases/ NOT in the Perimeter: Public Cloud Databases Web Hosting Cloud Databases Workaround: customer will be contacted to migrate to new Public Cloud Databases for PostgreSQL. Migration tutorials and Professional Services will be provided on https://docs.ovh.com/gb/en/enterprise-cloud-databases/ Timeline: 17/01/2022 10h CEST : End of Sales 16/05/2022 10h CEST : End of Growth 10/06/2022 10h-14h CEST : planned downtime 13/06/2022 10h CEST : End of Support, Shutdown of all impacted services 10h CEST We will update this task during the proposed timeline.

incident_updates.body: Start time : 28/03/2022 11:00 UTC End time : 28/03/2022 11:30 UTC Service impact : No impact expected on products already deployed. But there will be an unavailability of new product delivery for 1 min to 15 min maximum. Service improvement : The objective of this maintenance is to improve the Registry API backend.

incident_updates.body: [BHS3][Containers & Orchestration] - Storage Start time : 29/03/2022 08:00 UTC End time : 29/03/2022 14:00 UTC Service impact : This maintenance operation will prevent the scheduling of backups during the downtime (1 to 3 hours) of the Mistral service. Backups will be re-scheduled the next day as usual. Service improvement : The objective of this maintenance is to upgrade underlaying infrastructure.

Start time : 29/03/2022 08:00 UTC End time : 29/03/2022 16:00 UTC Service impact : No impact in production, only some connection timeout in the automation at the time of the intervention Service improvement: Migrate the current Pcc microservice from standalone container host to Kubernetes infrastructure

In order to improve the use of OVHStatus Public Cloud, we will redesign this space. The headings and products will correspond to the information and categories available in your manager.
We will proceed to this operation on Wednesday, April 06, 2022 from 10:00 UTC to 11:00 UTC.
All notification subscriptions will be reset to zero.
You will need to re-subscribe in order to receive product notifications.
Thank you for your understanding
